1932;;Charlie Chan's Chance;;American;;John G. Blystone;;Warner Oland, Marian Nixon, H. B. Warner;;drama, mystery;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlie_Chan%27s_Chance;;Charlie Chan is attending a police convention in New York City; he is an intended murder victim here, but avoids death by chance. To find his would-be-killer(s), Charlie must outguess police reps from both Scotland Yard and New York City Police.